text: Kerrigan, who was famously injured by an attack orchestrated by her competition, Harding in 1994, isn't phased by the tension between her and her co-star. “The level of competition is giving her so much motivation,” the source revealed of Kerrigan. “Nancy knows that Heather does not like her, but she is used to it. All it did was really force her to up her game this week because she does not want to get kicked off before Heather does!”
title: Watch Out! Heather Morris & Nancy Kerrigan's 'DWTS' Feud Just Got A Whole Lot Nastier

meta_data.description: Heather Morris and Nancy Kerrigan's feud on 'DWTS' just got a lot nastier. The actress is determined to beat the former Olympian.
